36
00:01:56,166 --> 00:01:58,633
<i>Seattle Grace
Mercy West Hospital.</i>

37
00:01:58,735 --> 00:02:02,337
<i>Home to some of the finest, most
influential doctors in the country.</i>

38
00:02:02,439 --> 00:02:04,990
<i>Several months ago, a
gunman roamed these halls,</i>

39
00:02:05,092 --> 00:02:07,442
<i>leaving 11 people dead
